SOURCE CODE:
package project3;
import java.util.Scanner;

public class Project3 {

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner input = new Scanner(System.in);
        int rev=0;
        int rem;
        System.out.print("Enter Number: ");
        int n = input.nextInt();
        while(n>0)
        {
        rem=n%10;
        rev=rev*10+rem;
        n=n/10;
        }
        System.out.println(rev);
  }
 }

OUTPUT:
Enter Number: 3467
7643

